column9:
Do you consider some of the categories below as important to mitigate climate change?
-Waste Management (recycling, waste reduction, waste decomposition etc.)
-Travel smart (use bikes, fly less, use public transport etc.)
-Eat sustainably (eat less meat, choose local and seasonal food etc.)
-Conserve Energy (turn off lights, reduce heating etc.)
